    "en": {
      "title": "The body of a girl was recovered from the minister's relative's house",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A hillbilly girl, who was working as a maid in a relative's house of Minister Prasanna Ranatunga, has been found dead from a swimming pool.",
        "A 17-year-old girl from Maskelia-Mocca Estate has been recovered as a dead body.",
        "He has been working at the home of the minister's younger father for the past six months.",
        "Gampaha and Maskelia police are carrying out investigations related to the incident while the police have said that they have got the CCTV footage of the girl slipping and falling in the swimming pool."
      ],
